offlineimap容易务删服务器邮件，如果本地邮箱删除，而~/.offlineimap目录又没删除，同步之后，服务器邮件全删
just delete ~/.offlineimap directory and the local mailboxes, then offlineimap sync 
在.muttrc里不要设置set record= and set postponed= 
mutt会把它们保存本地，然后同步到服务器上，但是当smtp时服务器上已经有了
所以会同步失败,等服务器同步到本地
getmail好像只能下载到一个文件夹，以为只能同步INBOX文件钾

所以多写几个配置在getmail里,需要首先搞清服务器上的文件钾名字，然后创建本地
同名文件钾，记得里面创建tmp cur new, 创建文件前，先删~/.getmail目录，然后创建~/.getmail目录和getmailrc并设置600,先删再建是为了清缓存记录
~/.getmail/getmailrc

[retriever]
type = SimpleIMAPSSLRetriever
server = imap.qq.com
port = 993
username = x
password = x
mailboxes = ("INBOX",)

[destination]
type = Maildir
path = /var/spool/john/INBOX/

[retriever]
type = SimpleIMAPSSLRetriever
server = imap.qq.com
port = 993
username = x
password = x
mailboxes = ("Sent Messages",)

[destination]
type = Maildir
path = /var/spool/john/Sent Messages/

[retriever]
type = SimpleIMAPSSLRetriever
server = imap.qq.com
port = 993
username = x
password = x
mailboxes = ("Drafts",)

[destination]
type = Maildir
path = /var/spool/john/Drafts/

[options]
read_all = false
delete = false
received = false
delivered_to = false
message_log = ~/.getmail/mvmail.log

